<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Die2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Die,</orth> subst., a small cube marked with numbers, used in gaming: <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.312" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 312</bibl> (quibbling with the verb <emph>to die</emph>). <bibl n="shak. wt 4.3.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 3, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.4.10" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 4, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.4.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 4, 34</bibl> (quibbling). Plural <cit><quote>dice:</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 1, 38</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.290" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 290</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.326" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 326</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.3.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 3, 33</bibl>. <cit><quote>to play at dice:</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 32</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 8</bibl>. <cit><quote>well run, dice!</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.233" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 233</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>